Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:09.10,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,So you've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.97,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Where's Armony?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.71,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.24,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:19.85,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Can't you see!? We're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.02,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,We’ll give the report later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.82,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I said wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.26,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:32.36,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,You see, I was asked not to let you two in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.73,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:39.00,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! Then I'll force my way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.10,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,We can't hold back! Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.07,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Please, just listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.01,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,How can I?! Armony's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.95,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\fs29}Think about Armony's feelings just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:54.02,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Armony's feelings...?
