Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.96,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1\4a&HFF&}My apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:06.13,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:11.30,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}If I can't even do that much, what kind of master am I?\NWhat's the point of alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.77,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:13.94,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:19.91,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.91,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Sure, we are kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:30.65,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}But... someday we'll grow up. Armony isn't like that.\NThe present is all she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.42,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I always knew a day like this would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:39.63,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2080)}Get out of my way!
